column2: "That... actually went better than expected. They probably won't chase us."
"Hey, partner? You've been looking that way the entire time we were fighting. Something over there caught your interest?"
"You heard someone's voice? If it was someone calling for help, then we'd better check it out."
"Well, it's up to you. I'll follow your lead, partner."
"What's wrong, partner? Is there something over there, too?"
"Hmmm...I've got a bad feeling about this, but if you're going that way, then I'll follow."
